---- MODULE PeerNegotiation ----
\* Per-peer WebRTC SDP offer/answer negotiation. Server is always the offerer.
\* Generated by tlaiser — https://github.com/hyperpolymath/tlaiser

EXTENDS Naturals, Sequences, TLC

\* State constants — each represents a distinct state
CONSTANTS Idle, Negotiating, Connected, Renegotiating

\* Variables tracked by this specification
VARIABLES state, pending_peer_count

\* Type invariant: state is always one of the declared states
TypeInvariant == state \in {Idle, Negotiating, Connected, Renegotiating}

\* Initial state predicate
Init ==
    /\ state = Idle
    /\ pending_peer_count = 0

\* Transition actions
\* Transition: Idle -> Negotiating (send_offer)
send_offer ==
    /\ state = Idle
    /\ state' = Negotiating
    /\ pending_peer_count := 0
    /\ UNCHANGED pending_peer_count

\* Transition: Negotiating -> Connected (sdp_answer_received)
sdp_answer_received ==
    /\ state = Negotiating
    /\ state' = Connected
    /\ UNCHANGED pending_peer_count

\* Transition: Negotiating -> Negotiating (peer_added_while_negotiating)
peer_added_while_negotiating ==
    /\ state = Negotiating
    /\ state' = Negotiating
    /\ pending_peer_count := pending_peer_count + 1
    /\ UNCHANGED pending_peer_count

\* Transition: Connected -> Renegotiating (peer_added_or_removed)
peer_added_or_removed ==
    /\ state = Connected
    /\ state' = Renegotiating
    /\ UNCHANGED pending_peer_count

\* Transition: Renegotiating -> Connected (sdp_answer_received)
sdp_answer_received ==
    /\ state = Renegotiating
    /\ state' = Connected
    /\ UNCHANGED pending_peer_count

\* Next-state relation: disjunction of all transitions
Next ==
    \/ send_offer
    \/ sdp_answer_received
    \/ peer_added_while_negotiating
    \/ peer_added_or_removed
    \/ sdp_answer_received

\* All variables tuple (for stuttering)
vars == <<state, pending_peer_count>>

\* Complete specification
Spec == Init /\ [][Next]_vars

\* Fair specification (with weak fairness on Next)
FairSpec == Spec /\ WF_vars(Next)

\* ---- Temporal Properties ----
\* Property: MutedParticipantNeverSpeaking (safety)
MutedParticipantNeverSpeaking == []([][ParticipantVoiceState = Muted => ~is_speaking]_ParticipantVoiceState)

\* Property: RoomNeverExceedsMaxParticipants (safety)
RoomNeverExceedsMaxParticipants == []([][participant_count <= max_participants]_participant_count)

\* Property: NegotiationEventuallyCompletes (liveness)
NegotiationEventuallyCompletes == <>(<>(PeerNegotiation = Connected))


====
